net-p2p/rslsync includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/rslsync

TO START ON BOOT:
# sysrc rslsync_enable=YES

START MANUALLY:
# service rslsync start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8888/

